CDM/111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c3413%2c20221207%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,111,聲,3413,20221207,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"3413","JDATE":"20221207","JTITLE":"定其應執行刑"}